00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,000
Fusion powers the Sun—so why can’t we capture it here?

2
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:04,800
The secret?

3
00:00:04,800 --> 00:00:09,200
It’s all about creating the right conditions: extreme temperature and pressure.

4
00:00:09,200 --> 00:00:14,400
Fusion needs over 150 million degrees Celsius—hotter than the core of the Sun!

5
00:00:14,400 --> 00:00:16,000
Can you imagine that?

6
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:21,600
Recent experiments have achieved net energy gain—big milestones—but commercial fusion is still years away.

7
00:00:21,600 --> 00:00:25,600
The DOE and ITER work tirelessly to conquer these challenges.

8
00:00:25,600 --> 00:00:28,800
Imagine a world powered by clean fusion energy!

9
00:00:28,800 --> 00:00:31,200
Curious about the future of energy?

